      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――星見まつり当日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（結局、今日まで千紗に）\n（誰とお祭りに行くのか聞けなかったな……）",
      "startTime": 4.2000001471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "屋台が沢山出てますね\n星見まつりのこの雰囲気、懐かしいです",
      "startTime": 10.26319741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "すまない。スケジュールに余裕があれば\nライブ前に会場を回れたんだが……",
      "startTime": 16.9666670044,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "気にしないで下さい。ライブの後に二人でお祭りを\n見に行く約束をしてますから",
      "startTime": 23.6432433644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……今日の相手とお祭りを見るのが\nそんなに楽しみなのか？",
      "startTime": 28.1333357056,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　私が実家を出て東京の寮に入ってからは\nなかなか会えなかったので……",
      "startTime": 35.5182559529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "今日は久しぶりに会えるのが凄く楽しみなんです",
      "startTime": 38.3182559529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか……遠距離は大変だな\nちなみに千紗はその人のどういうところが好きなんだ？",
      "startTime": 46.8000018637,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "好きなところですか？\nうーん……優しくて家族思いなところかな？",
      "startTime": 53.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "本人は周りからよく「お前は娘に甘過ぎる」って\n言われてるみたいです",
      "startTime": 63.2179414946,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと待て、娘だって？\nその男には子供がいるのか！？　歳はいくつなんだ？",
      "startTime": 67.1000026266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "年齢ですか？　ええと、今年でよんじゅう……",
      "startTime": 71.1320233541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "四十代！？　あーなんてことだ！\n千紗とは親子ほど年が離れているじゃないか！",
      "startTime": 80.2000066956,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "こいつは思っていたより大事だぞ！",
      "startTime": 83.2288975277,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "親子ほどというか……親子ですけど……",
      "startTime": 86.3221409199,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いくら親子だからって、四十代子持ちの男が\n女子高生の千紗となんて社会的に……え？　親子？",
      "startTime": 92.933340029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "様子がおかしいと思ったら\nそういうことだったんですね……",
      "startTime": 103.454684897,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "もうっ、私は付き合ってる男の人なんていませんから\n変な誤解をしないで下さい！",
      "startTime": 110.6546879488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんにだけは\nそういう勘違いをされたくないです！",
      "startTime": 114.9213500379,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "すまなかった……。確かに、昔はよく父親と\n夏祭りに来ていたと話していたな",
      "startTime": 121.5000051698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "そうです。だから、久しぶりにお父さんと\nお祭りに行けるのが凄く嬉しいんです",
      "startTime": 127.6758624115,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、そうだったのか……\n疑ってすまない、悪かった",
      "startTime": 134.3000051698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "……いえ、それだけ私のことを\n心配してくれたんですよね",
      "startTime": 141.1307353692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "もし、まだ私のことが心配なら\n一緒にお祭りを回りますか？",
      "startTime": 148.0307353692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-evening"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "いや、俺はサニピの他の四人と回るから\n千紗は親子水入らずで楽しんでくるといい",
      "startTime": 154.2000031353,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました。{user}さんも\nお祭りを楽しんできて下さい",
      "startTime": 160.2144537644,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-out-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3800.0000000000114,
          "startTime": 164.0144537644
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（いよいよ星見まつりのイベントライブ開始だ）\n（最初から凄い盛り上がりで文字通りのお祭り騒ぎだな）",
      "startTime": 168.366669802,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-out-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7499.996459400023,
          "startTime": 175.8666662614
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_02-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん、星見まつり楽しんでますか？\nお祭りの雰囲気ってワクワクしちゃいますよね",
      "startTime": 176.8588299152,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
